policies.policyname: Users can insert staging data to their holding
policies.with_check:
(holding_id IN ( SELECT uh.holding_id
   FROM (user_holdings uh
     JOIN users u ON ((u.id = uh.user_id)))
  WHERE (u.auth_id = auth.uid())))
